<p>When I dropped the coconut balls into the chocolate they melted some, making the chocolate tricky to stick.  Plus mine stayed as balls because when I tried to smash them they fell apart (I didn't use a mini scoop though so my forms weren't solid).  They don't look pretty but they taste great.  Thanks for the refined-sugar-free recipe!</p>
